sentences.en: It uses this to interpret the interrelationship of the patterns and draw conclusions that allow us to identify people and places.
sentences.cn: 它利用这一点来解释模式的相互关系，并得出结论，使我们能够识别人和地方。

sentences.en: Culture exercises an crucial influence over social interrelationship.
sentences.cn: 文化对社会相互关系有重要影响。

sentences.en: Coupling refers to the interrelationship (s) of components (or objects) in an application.
sentences.cn: 耦合即应用程序中各组件(或各对象)间的相互关系。
